⚠️ Very Important Interview Question

Interviewer may ask:

What problem happens if new records are inserted while paginating?

Correct answer:

Cursor-based pagination is more stable than offset-based pagination because it paginates based on actual data values instead of row positions, reducing duplication or missing records when inserts happen.

